action_extraction.template:
Analyze the following email and extract all action items, tasks, and deadlines.

Email Content:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

Extract:
1. Specific tasks or action items requested
2. Deadlines or due dates (if mentioned)
3. Priority level (high/medium/low)

Respond in JSON format:
{
  "tasks": [
    {
      "task": "description of the task",
      "deadline": "specific date or 'None' if not mentioned",
      "priority": "high/medium/low"
    }
  ]
}

If no action items are found, return: {"tasks": []}

