urgency_analysis.template:
Analyze the urgency level of this email on a scale of 1-5:

1 = Not urgent (can wait days/weeks)
2 = Low urgency (can wait a few days)
3 = Medium urgency (should respond within 1-2 days)
4 = High urgency (should respond within 24 hours)
5 = Critical urgency (requires immediate attention)

Email Content:
From: {sender}
Subject: {subject}
Body: {body}

Respond with:
{
  "urgency_score": [1-5],
  "reason": "brief explanation",
  "suggested_response_time": "timeframe"
}
